A middle-aged man in a crisp white lab coat stands in a futuristic beauty clinic, surrounded by sleek chrome skincare devices with glowing blue panels, while his reflection in a polished mirror shows him simultaneously typing on a vintage computer keyboard. The scene is split diagonally—one half bathed in soft pink salon lighting with elegant curved furniture, the other half in the cool blue glow of server room monitors displaying cascading data streams. Neon accents in magenta and cyan frame the composition. The man has an amused, knowing expression as he holds a high-tech facial wand in one hand. Cyberpunk style with sharp contrasts, rain-streaked windows in the background revealing Singapore's iconic skyline at night, and holographic product displays floating in the air.
